research_municipality_step.notes: San Antonio operates under a council-manager form of government, where the mayor and city council are elected, and a city manager is appointed. The 'mayor_council' government type was chosen as the closest fit among the provided options, as the mayor is an integral part of the elected council. Gina Ortiz Jones assumed office as Mayor on June 18, 2025. The city council members listed are based on recent election information and official city sources.
